    "en": {
      "title": "Announcement regarding power outage",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Public Utilities Commission informed that a 3-hour power cut will be implemented today and tomorrow.",
        "A to L and P to W zones will have power cut for one hour and 40 minutes during day and one hour and 20 minutes at night.",
        "It has been announced that there will be a power cut for 2 hours and 30 minutes from 6.00 am to 8.30 am in Colombo city areas.",
        "Also, it has been announced that there will be power cut for 3 hours from 5.30 am to 8.30 am in MNOXYZ zones."
      ],
